sections.heading: vehicle sale; violation; penalty
sections.text: Any person guilty of violating any of the provisions of section 60-1417 shall be guilty of a Class III misdemeanor.SourceLaws 1945, c. 143, § 10, p. 463;R.R.S.1943, § 60-618;Laws 1963, c. 365, § 14, p. 1179;Laws 1971, LB 768, § 37;Laws 1977, LB 39, § 96.
